reviewText: It's a funny movie. The bathroom scene reminds me of The Naked Gun.
A little obvious at times, but still a funny movie... brings a lot of the "Get Smart" from the Sixties to the present...

The movie itself is very funny. My review is for the damage to the Blu Ray case the movie arrived in. Shattered beyond repair. I would have immediately returned the movie if I had not had spare cases to place the movie in.
